    "Name": "Wolf Trap",
    "Details": "A mid-Jihad testbed design of the Wolf Trap, this 'Mech was used to test out Experimental Technologies under the supervision of Akihisa Inoue. This test model retains most of the 'Mech's equipment, however it replaced all of the weapons and armor. Its standard armor was replaced by 8 tons of ferro-fibrous armor, and is armament consists of an Experimental silver bullet Gauss rifle with 2 tons of ammunition backed up by a pair of experimental medium X-Pulse lasers. The 'Mech's heat sinks were replaced by double heat sinks.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Upper</color>",
